James Creag suffers from the condition Erythropoietic Protoporphyria . 
  Suffers from terrible sunburn when exposed to sunlight . 
  He must use a special brown suncream to protect his skin from the sun . 
  But he has been racially abused in the street because of the cream . 
  He is so sick of being taunted that he has stopped wearing it . 
  He has to wear the cream because his skin cannot be exposed to direct sunlight . 
 